OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776877554
OL,3,CNI Water appears before MLAs to
OL,4,Cdiscuss its impact on Lough Neagh
OL,5,Cpollution
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland Water revealed it is
OL,8,Fresponsible for 20% of the total
OL,9,Famount of one of the main chemicals
OL,10,Fcausing pollution in Lough Neagh each
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThe company revealed to MLAs today in
OL,14,Fa joint Agriculture and Infrastructure
OL,15,FCommittee that its actions account for
OL,16,Froughly 70 tonnes of phosphorus
OL,17,Fentering the lough each year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
