CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776877554
OL,3,CNI Water appears before MLAs to
OL,4,Cdiscuss its impact on Lough Neagh
OL,5,Cpollution
OL,7,FWith other causes including
OL,8,Fagriculture, warmer weather and urban
OL,9,Frun-off.
OL,11,FWhile the list of contributors is
OL,12,Flong, the time needed to improve the
OL,13,Fsituation is likely to take even
OL,14,Flonger.
